```

#### Implementation 8:
```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * np.mean(bins)) + np.cos(np.pi * item / bins) + np.exp(item - np.mean(bins))
```

#### Implementation 9:
```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item - np.max(bins)) * (item * np.std(bins)) + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins)
```

#### Implementation 10:
```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * np.log(bins + 1)) + np.cos(np.pi * item / bins) + np.exp(item - np.mean(bins))
```

